      <div xml:id="ASimplePlan"> 
              <interpGrp type="poembox">
                <interp ana="#form" type="haiku"></interp>
                <interp ana="#tone" type="sad"></interp>
                <interp ana="#topic" type="love"></interp>
              </interpGrp>
             <lg> 
              <l>Simple Sam was a simple man.</l>
          <l>He lived each day by a simple plan.</l> 
          <l>Enjoy your life and live while you can.</l>
          <l>Make each day count and take a stand.</l>
          <l>Stand on the left or stand on the right,</l>
          <l>Whichever one you think is right.</l>
          <l>Live each day as if your last.</l>
          <l>Life's too short and gone too fast.</l>
         
                 
